'''3月0日'''是[[3月|3月]]第一天的前一天，[[2月|2月]]的最後一天。這一表述可以用於軟件，如[[Microsoft_Excel|Microsoft Excel]]中來容納月份的變量長度和[[闰年|闰年]]。<ref>{{citation|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=tZ7ss5KihJ0C&pg=PT144|title=Strategic Business Forecasting: A Structured Approach to Shaping the Future|author=Simon Ramo, Ronald Sugar|language=en|accessdate=2010-04-01|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103115930/http://books.google.com/books?id=tZ7ss5KihJ0C&pg=PT144|dead-url=no}}</ref>

「3月0日」有時被[[天文學家|天文學家]]用作2月最後一天的同義詞。<ref>{{citation|title=Astronomical Almanac for the year 2003|date=2001|publisher=U.S Government Printing Office and The Stationery Office|location=Washington and London|page=K2|language=en}}</ref>

